data.description: Check out this great home in the heart of Southgate! This home has new flooring on main floor, newer hot water heater, off street parking with a long driveway and a great fenced in backyard! 2 bedrooms on the main floor with a full bathroom. The unfinished basement also offers 2 additional flex rooms that could be used as an office and/or bedrooms plus another full bath that is ready for your finishing touches! This home could also be a great investment property if used as a short or long term rental! Also, check out that city view from the front of the house! Minutes to shops, restaurants, the Levee and downtown Cincinnati! Great location! Call for your showing today!
